	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64285792">The important things unions can fight for change as our society changes and not everything will be covered by law.<br>
One of the great things a union can do is to stand for the individual that gets in a conflict with a financially much stronger employer, most employees can never afford the type of legal support a company can.</div>
